subject: ENGLISH
text: Write a composition of about three pages in length on any one of the following subjects:

subject: ENGLISH
text: The Garden in Spring and in Autumn.

subject: ENGLISH
text: My First Play or My First Film or My First Football Match.

subject: ENGLISH
text: “A policeman's lot is not a happy one.” Is this true?

subject: ENGLISH
text: Describe a radio or a television programme which particularly appeals to you, and give reasons for your choice.

subject: ENGLISH
text: The joy of possessing a new book or a new camera or a new dress or a new suit of clothes or a new bicycle or a new set of golf clubs or a new kit of tools or a new tennis racket.

subject: ENGLISH
text: A story in which the outcome turns upon the toss of a coin.

subject: ENGLISH
text: Describe an incident in which Macavity might have taken part.
